    // We break the cycle by fixing the state of element 0.

    // DP state: dp[i][0] = minimum cost using a subset of {0, 1, ..., i} where element i is NOT selected.
    // dp[i][1] = minimum cost using a subset of {0, 1, ..., i} where element i IS selected.

